TITLE: Faceted Crystal Glass White Resin Necklace Earrings Set
DESCRIPTION:
This fun, sparkling necklace is a combination of several sizes of faceted clear crystal glass beads, two large diamond-shaped gray glass beads and white resin beads.  The one inch large center faceted crystal glass bead is surrounded with small faceted crystal glass beads and silver plated bead bars.  

I finished the 21 inch necklace with a large diamond link sterling silver chain and a cute sterling silver hook and eye clasp.  The length of the link chain can be shorter or longer.   Please contact me before ordering.

Matching earrings are dangling from sterling silver ear wires - length is 1.5 inches.  All other materials for the necklace and earrings are sterling silver.

This unique, chunky and funky necklace set will dress up any outfit, stunning.  You won't be disappointed.
MATERIALS: 30mm oval clear crystal glass bead,6mm round clear crystal glass beads,20mm round white resin beads,15mm round white resin beads,12mm round white resin beads,10mm x 16mm crystal glass oval faceted beads,15mm clear crystal faceted roundel beads,6mm clear crystal faceted roundel beads,30mm gray diamond shaped glasss beads,20mm silver plated bead bars,5mm  diamond link sterling silver chain,20mm sterling silver hook and eye clasp,sterling silver findings
